{"tid":1377043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"根據警察通例守則 忌於內街使用催淚毒氣","createTime":"2019-07-28T12:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T16:52:59.000Z","uid":147010,"like":128,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"d1787288c7880648a80c045dc5bb600db41ebfd7","tid":1377043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:51:38.000Z","msg":"警察有通例守則，(理應)避免於狹窄巷道，內街使用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wb40oO5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWb40oO5.png&h=d7e53adb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好理佢地仲會唔會遵守<br />\n一齊諗下點樣借呢樣野去智破困局，發酵輿論。唔好浪費前線留比我地嘅機會去入佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">警方繼元朗事件後再一次妄顧市民安危</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DKTcZok.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDKTcZok.png&h=7c549f77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">根據指引，要淨化CS(催淚煙霧)係非常困難而且重要。</span></span><br />\n以上3點淨化工作視乎程度有可能需要重覆數次。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">懷疑受污染食物，不論有否包裝都理應拋棄</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請大家話比元朗，西環及其他受過催淚煙霧影響嘅地方居民知。"},{"pid":"0e9ee8c3b748b3c75b9fc43ba5a0399abffe20b3","tid":1377043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:54:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23e60d599a1f36b7856e820d84ded3003f75b999","tid":1377043,"uid":78349,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:57:30.000Z","msg":"海味舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d59491aad99f2369bf4566eb35d25f7125607a","tid":1377043,"uid":155374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:59:11.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解唔跟警察通例？<br />\n因為果啲唔係警察囉"},{"pid":"1f36363ec0fb761c8109fb18705dd2af9055f3d8","tid":1377043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu